translation.Name: Belgium Note - Herstal Factory #1
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: Weapon production will not stop, but be increased.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_3: The Belgian Military ordered a mass-production of weapons to help fight the zombie virus from spreading.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: Tomorrow at noon the Belgian Military will arrive at the factory to receive at least 10,000 rounds in military and ranger ammunition.
